<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Soundshift</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Helvetica;
            margin: 0;
            padding-left:0px;
            padding-right:0px;
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            flex-direction: column;
            background: linear-gradient(-135deg, #7e2ffc, #26acff);
            background-color: rgb(53, 53, 145);
            background-attachment: fixed; /* Keeps the background fixed */
            background-size: 100% 100%; /* Scales the background to cover the entire viewport */
}


        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 25px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .navbar ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .navbar li {
            color: #261f37;
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 40px;
            font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .navbar li a {
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
            color: inherit; /* Inherit the text color from the parent element */
        }

        .navbar li:hover a {
            cursor: pointer;
            color: yellow;
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #224189;
        }

        .content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            max-width: 1200px;
        }

        .left-side {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding:50px;
        }

        .right-side {
            overflow-y: hidden; /* Hide vertical overflow */
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding:50px;
        }

        .circle-inner {
            width: 450px;
            height: 450px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: -webkit-radial-gradient(65% 15%, circle, white 1px, aqua 3%, darkblue 60%, aqua 100%); 
            background: -moz-radial-gradient(65% 15%, circle, white 1px, aqua 3%, darkblue 60%, aqua 100%); 
            background: -o-radial-gradient(65% 15%, circle, white 1px, aqua 3%, darkblue 60%, aqua 100%);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 65% 15%, white 1px, aqua 3%, darkblue 60%, aqua 100%);       
            transition: opacity 0.5s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 100px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .circle-inner:hover {
            cursor: pointer;
            background: -webkit-radial-gradient(65% 15%, circle, white 1px, aqua 3%, darkblue 60%, aqua 100%); 
            background: -moz-radial-gradient(65% 15%, circle, white 1px, aqua 3%, darkblue 60%, aqua 100%); 
            background: -o-radial-gradient(65% 15%, circle, white 1px, aqua 3%, darkblue 60%, aqua 100%);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 65% 15%, white 1px, aqua 3%, darkblue 60%, aqua 100%);       
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .square-inner {
            overflow-y: auto; /* Allow vertical scroll */
            width: 700px;
            height: 500px;
            background-color: #e9e9e9;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 10px rgba(72, 72, 72, 0.3);
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .footer {
            color: #91aaff;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .circle-label {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body><center>
    <div class="navbar">
        <h1 style="
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica Neue;
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: -20px; 
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: yellow;
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #224189;
            transform: perspective(100px) rotateX(15deg);
            ">SOUNDSHIFT</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="navbar">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/mainpage">Home</a></li>
            <li>Profile</li>
            <li>Settings</li>
            <li><a href="/logout">Log Out</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="left-side">
            <div class="circle-inner">
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="right-side">
            <div class="square-inner">
                <h1 style="text-align: center;color:#393939; font-family: Helvetica Neue" >Submit a fav song:</h1>
                
                <!-- Song Title -->
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label for="songTitle">Song Title:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="songTitle" name="songTitle">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="explicit" name="explicit">
                    <label for="explicit">Explicit</label>
                </div>
    
                <!-- Artist Name -->
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label for="artistName">Artist Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="artistName" name="artistName">
                </div>
    
                <!-- Genre -->
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <label for="genre">Genre:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="genre" name="genre">
                </div>
    
                <div>
                    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                </div>
                
                <h1 style="text-align: center;color:#393939; font-family: Helvetica Neue">How it works:</h1>
                <p style="font-family: Helvetica Light;">Soundshift provides a user-friendly way for people to make their music experience more diverse. By
                    simply pressing the “Shift” button, users can instantly access a randomly selected song, breaking the
                    cycle of repetitive music listening.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    

    <div class="footer">
        Made by: Valentino Ivanovski for Systems 3 - 2024
    </div>
</body>
</html>
